。</p><p>激进的升级并不令人惊讶。 Polestar 现在面临比 2 首次接触客户时更激烈的竞争，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/teslas-latest-price-cut-brings-model-3-pricing-below-40000-071124983.html">价格较低的 Tesla Model 3</a> （目前起价为 40,240 美元）。改进后的电动汽车可能比其最明显的竞争对手成本更高，但您也可以获得更长的续航里程和更多的安全功能。性能也大致相当。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-more-powerful-2024-polestar-2-starts-at-49900-151559369.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-more-powerful-2024-polestar-2-starts-at-49900-151559369.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8a9299bb-711b-4606-a2cc-18f714c10361</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 15:15:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686670340</ingested><modified> 2023-06-13T15:32:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1225" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/622a3db0-09ff-11ee-bbee-5b483c1d1544" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1225" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/622a3db0-09ff-11ee-bbee-5b483c1d1544" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Polestar]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The 2024 Polesta